k.com/skinbyretrouve/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@officialretrouve\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTikTok\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat: \u003c/strong\u003eA small-batch \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/luxury\"\u003eluxury\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin-care\u003c/a\u003e brand formulated with ingredients from the founders\u0026#39; family farm. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range:\u003c/strong\u003e $45-$415\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounders:\u003c/strong\u003e Jami and Klaus Heidegger\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story:\u003c/strong\u003e Founded by Jami and Klaus Heidegger in 2014 and now joined by their daughter, Hannah, Retrouvé (French for \u0026#34;to find again\u0026#34;) combines \u0026#34;highly effective ingredients in elevated concentrations\u0026#34; with \u0026#34;luxurious, skin-supporting formulas.\u0026#34; \u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn creating Retrouvé, the founders harnessed their lineage — and four generations of skin-care knowledge — as the family behind Kiehl\u0026#39;s Since 1851. Jami developed these powerful, gender-neutral products for their own use only and never intended on selling them, but their friends and family started asking for them and the demand grew. Over the years, Jami evolved and refined the formulations as new technologies became available.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRetrouvé\u0026#39;s collection of multi-purpose products address skin dehydration, roughness, dullness, fine lines and wrinkles. Jami and the Retrouvé team innovated the trademarked Triple Airless Protection System (RTAPS313), which is \u0026#34;a technologically advanced, airless manufacturing process and delivery system that help prevent ingredients from degrading prematurely, remaining potent and stable for maximum efficacy.\u0026#34; The brand creates products in small batches and harvests ingredients directly from its \u0026#34;sustainable permaculture family farm,\u0026#34; Palms of Malibu.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1045px) 1045px, calc(33vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_127/MjExOTgwMzAwNTIyMjM1NDI3/retrouve-revitalizing-eye-concentrate-skin-hydrator.webp 127w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_207/MjExOTgwMzAwNTIyMjM1NDI3/retrouve-revitalizing-eye-concentrate-skin-hydrator.webp 207w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_234/MjExOTgwMzAwNTIyMjM1NDI3/retrouve-revitalizing-eye-concentrate-skin-hydrator.webp 234w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_414/MjExOTgwMzAwNTIyMjM1NDI3/retrouve-revitalizing-eye-concentrate-skin-hydrator.webp 414w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_467/MjExOTgwMzAwNTIyMjM1NDI3/retrouve-revitalizing-eye-concentrate-skin-hydrator.webp 467w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1045px) 1045px, calc(33vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_127/MjExOTgwMzAwNTIyMjM1NDI3/retrouve-revitalizing-eye-concentrate-skin-hydrator.jpg 127w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:141%2Cc